## 2026-04-05 - manual-snapshot.ts quarantined sets never added to completedSets
- Fixed: when a set exceeds MAX_RECOVERY_RETRIES during crash recovery, it is now added to `journal.completedSets` and the journal is written to disk before the `continue`. This prevents the quarantined set from re-appearing in `pending` on every subsequent server restart.
